value.string: This home is meant for a chef! The kitchen features a massive island with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, upgraded backsplash and a walk-in pantry. The home also has hardwood flooring throughout the main level and a large screened in patio that looks out on a wooded tree buffer. Home is currently under construction and will be complete in May 2016. Photos include some from a staged model home. Come visit the model home located at 201 Durants Neck; it's open 7 days a week.

From I-40, take exit 282 for Page Rd. Turn right at the light. Go straight until it becomes Hopson Rd. Turn Left onto Keystone Park Drive. Go straight until it becomes Church Street. Home is in Everett Crossing subdivision (on the right).

116 Traphill Drive is a condo in Morrisville, NC 27560. This 1627 square foot condo sits on a 0.06 lot and features 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms. Built in 2016, this condo has been on the market for a total of 39 days and is currently priced at 251890.
